<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_matsa_tasquatch.messinWithTasquatch</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>messinWithTasquatch</name><script><![CDATA[var messinWithTasquatch = Class.create();
messinWithTasquatch.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {

    },

    syncOldTasqs: function() {
        var taskImportObj = {};
        var tasqImportRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_tasquatch_tasq_import');
        tasqImportRec.addQuery('active', true);
        tasqImportRec.query();
        while (tasqImportRec.next()) {

            var out_of_syncThresholdSeconds = tasqImportRec.out_of_sync_threshold_in_minutes * -60;
            var outOfSyncThreshold = new GlideDateTime(tasqImportRec.last_sync);
            outOfSyncThreshold.addSeconds(out_of_syncThresholdSeconds);

            taskImportObj[tasqImportRec.getUniqueValue()] = {
                import: tasqImportRec.getUniqueValue(),
                out_of_syncThreshold: outOfSyncThreshold,

            }

        }

        // Loop through imports to find out of sync tasqs
        for (var taskImport in taskImportObj) {
            var tasq = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_tasquatch_tasquatch');
            tasq.addEncodedQuery("last_sync<=" + taskImportObj[taskImport].out_of_syncThreshold + "^tasq_import=" + taskImportObj[taskImport].import+'^tasquatch_status=in_sync');
            tasq.query();

            while (tasq.next()) {

                this.syncTasq(tasq, 'not_syncing')
            }
        }
    },

    syncTasq: function(tasq, successStatus) {
        var endpoints = {},
            runTime = new GlideDateTime();

        // Get  Endpoint
        var endpointRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_tasquatch_endpoints');
        if (endpointRec.get(tasq.getValue('endpoint'))) {

            //Get Tasq Import
            var tasqImportRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_tasquatch_tasq_import');
            if (tasqImportRec.get(tasq.getValue('tasq_import'))) {

                // Build object for use in fetching record
                endpoints[tasq.getUniqueValue()] = {
                    'remote_instance': endpointRec.remote_instance + '',
                    'user_name': endpointRec.user_name + '',
                    'password': endpointRec.password.getDecryptedValue() + '',
                    'sys_id': endpointRec.getUniqueValue() + '',
                    "tasqImports": {}
                };

                // Build query info
                endpoints[tasq.getUniqueValue()].tasqImports[tasqImportRec.getUniqueValue()] = {
                    'sys_id': tasqImportRec.getUniqueValue() + '',
                    'table_name': tasqImportRec.table_name + '',
                    'table_query': 'sys_id=' + tasq.tasq_sys_id,
                    'tasq_name': tasqImportRec.tasq_name + ''
                };
                // Get the recs

                var tasqs = this.getTasqs(endpoints[tasq.getUniqueValue()], endpoints[tasq.getUniqueValue()].tasqImports[tasqImportRec.getUniqueValue()]);

                var tasqsObj = JSON.parse(tasqs);
                var endpoint = tasq.getUniqueValue()

                for (var tasq in tasqsObj.result) {

                    this.updateTasqs(tasqsObj.result[tasq], endpoints[endpoint], endpoints[endpoint].tasqImports[tasqImportRec.getUniqueValue()], successStatus);
                }

            } else {
                // Error getting Tasq Import REc
                gs.error('Error getting Tasq Import Rec')
            }
        } else {
            // Error getting Endpoint
            gs.error('Error getting Endpoint')
        }
    },

    syncTasqs: function() {

        var endpointArr = [],
            endpoints = {},
            runTime = new GlideDateTime();
        // Get all Endpoints
        var endpointRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_tasquatch_endpoints');
        endpointRec.addQuery('active', true);
        endpointRec.query();
        while (endpointRec.next()) {
            endpoints[endpointRec.getUniqueValue()] = {
                'remote_instance': endpointRec.remote_instance + '',
                'user_name': endpointRec.user_name + '',
                'password': endpointRec.password.getDecryptedValue() + '',
                'sys_id': endpointRec.getUniqueValue() + '',
                'tasqImports': {}
            };

            endpointArr.push(endpointRec.getUniqueValue());
        }

        // Get all Imports for each endpoint
        var tasqImportRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_tasquatch_tasq_import');
        tasqImportRec.addQuery('active', true);
        tasqImportRec.addEncodedQuery('endpoint.sys_idIN' + endpointArr.join());
        tasqImportRec.query();
        while (tasqImportRec.next()) {

            var currRun = new GlideDateTime().getNumericValue();
            var lastRun = new GlideDateTime(tasqImportRec.last_sync).getNumericValue();
            var syncInterval = tasqImportRec.sync_interval_in_minutes;
            var currInterval = (currRun - lastRun) / 1000 / 60;

            if (parseInt(currInterval) > parseInt(syncInterval)) {

                endpoints[tasqImportRec.endpoint + ''].tasqImports[tasqImportRec.getUniqueValue()] = {
                    'sys_id': tasqImportRec.getUniqueValue() + '',
                    'table_name': tasqImportRec.table_name + '',
                    'table_query': tasqImportRec.table_query + '',
                    'tasq_name': tasqImportRec.tasq_name + ''
                };
                tasqImportRec.last_sync = new GlideDateTime();
                tasqImportRec.update();
            }
        }


        for (var endpoint in endpoints) {

            for (var tasqImport in endpoints[endpoint].tasqImports) {

                if (endpoints[endpoint].tasqImports[tasqImport].table_name) {
                    // Get the recs
                    var tasqs = this.getTasqs(endpoints[endpoint], endpoints[endpoint].tasqImports[tasqImport]);

                    var tasqsObj = JSON.parse(tasqs);

                    for (var tasq in tasqsObj.result) {

                        this.updateTasqs(tasqsObj.result[tasq], endpoints[endpoint], endpoints[endpoint].tasqImports[tasqImport]);
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    },


    getTasqs: function(endPoint, tasqImport) {

        var request = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
        request.setEndpoint(encodeURI("https://" + endPoint.remote_instance + ".service-now.com/api/now/table/" + tasqImport.table_name + "?sysparm_query=" + tasqImport.table_query.toString() + '&sysparm_display_value=all'));
        request.setHttpMethod('GET');

        var user = endPoint.user_name;
        var password = endPoint.password;

        request.setBasicAuth(user, password);
        request.setRequestHeader("Accept", "application/json");

        var response = request.execute();
        var respBody = response.getBody();

        return respBody;
    },

    updateTasqs: function(tasq, endPoint, tasqImport, successStatus) {
        var updatedTask = false;
        var relatedRecord = "https://" + endPoint.remote_instance + ".service-now.com/" + tasq.sys_class_name.value + ".do?sys_id=" + tasq.sys_id.value;
        var tasqRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_tasquatch_tasquatch');

        // If the tasq has previously been mapped update the object only
        if (tasqRec.get('related_record', relatedRecord)) {
            tasqRec.task_obj = JSON.stringify(tasq);
            tasqRec.last_sync = new GlideDateTime();
            if (successStatus)
                tasqRec.tasquatch_status = successStatus;
            updatedTask = tasqRec.update();
        }

        // If the tasq has not previously been mapped create a new Tasq
        else {
            tasqRec.initialize();
            tasqRec.type = tasq.sys_class_name.display_value;
            tasqRec.related_record = relatedRecord;
            tasqRec.task_obj = JSON.stringify(tasq);
            tasqRec.endpoint = endPoint.sys_id;
            tasqRec.tasq_import = tasqImport.sys_id;
            tasqRec.tasq_sys_id = tasq.sys_id.value;
            tasqRec.last_sync = new GlideDateTime();
            tasqRec.tasquatch_status = 'in_sync';
            updatedTask = tasqRec.insert();
        }
        return updatedTask;
    },

    type: 'messinWithTasquatch'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>brent.llewellyn</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-05-24 11:38:03</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>75124f45db9e53005dbe38f0ad961917</sys_id><sys_mod_count>30</sys_mod_count><sys_name>messinWithTasquatch</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Tasquatch" source="x_matsa_tasquatch">ed3b6a4adbb51700497856f3ce961949</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Tasquatch">ed3b6a4adbb51700497856f3ce961949</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_75124f45db9e53005dbe38f0ad961917</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>brent.llewellyn</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-05-24 16:12:37</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
